<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,224,290]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,217,224,250]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Note.</emphasis>
Species here considered as 
<taxonomicName box="[551,708,225,250]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Leptodrassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[551,708,225,250]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Leptodrassus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are only those with the peculiar cheliceral dentition found in the type-species 
<taxonomicName box="[346,450,264,289]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Leptodrassus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femineus">
<emphasis box="[346,450,264,289]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">femineus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<figureCitation box="[466,538,264,290]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="5.[151,255,1833,1857]" captionTargetBox="[251,1334,495,1795]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[238,1348,467,1807]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 8. Leptodrassus femineus Simon, 1873, Ψ, right chela with retromarginal characteristic teeth; inner view. FIGURES 9 – 11. Leptodrassus femineus Simon, 1873, ♂, left palpus. 9. Ventral view. 10. Retrolateral view. 11. Tibia and cymbium (in part), dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/186956/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Fig. 
<number box="[521,538,264,290]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
; cf. 
<bibRefCitation author="Murphy" box="[589,760,264,290]" pageId="6" pageNumber="49" refString="Murphy, J. A. (2007) Gnaphosid genera of the world. British Arachnological Society, St Neots, Cambs, 2 Volumes, 1 - 605." type="journal article" year="2007">
Murphy, 
<number box="[696,760,264,290]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" value="2007.0">2007</number>
</bibRefCitation>
). None has been reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[1128,1193,264,290]" name="Israel" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Israel</collectingCountry>
until now.
